01:10:05.051 --> 01:10:06.051
It's not me.

01:10:07.083 --> 01:10:09.117
- None of this is you.

01:10:09.117 --> 01:10:10.880
You haven't been you
in months, not since...

01:10:10.880 --> 01:10:12.332
- Yeah, not since it all happened.

01:10:12.332 --> 01:10:14.156
You should have just let me be.

01:10:14.156 --> 01:10:16.923
You could have died quietly and alone,

01:10:16.923 --> 01:10:18.622
then we wouldn't be here now would we?

01:10:18.622 --> 01:10:20.683
- Don't do that.

01:10:20.683 --> 01:10:22.686
- Do what?

01:10:22.686 --> 01:10:24.300
- Cheapen everything.

01:10:24.300 --> 01:10:25.986
- Oh, that's all memories are anymore.

01:10:25.986 --> 01:10:26.819
Cheap.

01:10:41.304 --> 01:10:42.412
- Hey, ,

01:10:42.412 --> 01:10:44.329
but she's not here man.

01:10:46.521 --> 01:10:48.955
- Where is she?

01:10:48.955 --> 01:10:51.232
- Scott, look, I told you,

01:10:51.232 --> 01:10:53.073
I don't know, man, I haven't seen her.

01:10:54.752 --> 01:10:57.920
Jesus, what the hell is wrong with you?

01:10:57.920 --> 01:10:58.919
- I'll pop you again,

01:10:58.919 --> 01:10:59.930
where the hell is she?

01:10:59.930 --> 01:11:00.847
- Not here.

01:11:02.046 --> 01:11:04.592
- She lies, Tim.

01:11:04.592 --> 01:11:06.610
I told you that.

01:11:06.610 --> 01:11:08.512
- Yeah, you said a lot of shit.

01:11:08.512 --> 01:11:11.247
- Yeah and it was all true,

01:11:11.247 --> 01:11:15.042
except the part about you being my friend.

01:11:15.042 --> 01:11:16.676
- I am.

01:11:16.676 --> 01:11:18.224
I'm the only one you've got.

01:11:18.224 --> 01:11:19.951
- Then listen to me.

01:11:19.951 --> 01:11:21.504
Because everything that has happened,

01:11:21.504 --> 01:11:24.180
everything that has happened to me,

01:11:24.180 --> 01:11:27.180
what I did, it's all because of her.

01:11:29.103 --> 01:11:30.960
- Well, then, turn yourself in, man.

01:11:30.960 --> 01:11:32.543
Bring her down too.

01:11:34.096 --> 01:11:36.224
- There's no point.

01:11:36.224 --> 01:11:39.937
It's her or me, one of us is gonna die,

01:11:39.937 --> 01:11:41.770
right here, right now.

01:11:43.424 --> 01:11:45.023
- Completely lost your mind.

01:11:45.023 --> 01:11:45.856
- No, no.

01:11:48.368 --> 01:11:49.785
I found my peace.

01:11:51.872 --> 01:11:54.039
In the worst possible way.

01:11:58.050 --> 01:12:01.050
- Scott, please, man, just sit down.

01:12:03.952 --> 01:12:04.785
Okay?

01:12:08.576 --> 01:12:09.951
Son of a bitch.

01:12:14.944 --> 01:12:16.722
You really should have believed me, Tim.

01:12:16.722 --> 01:12:18.389
I'm not the bad guy.

01:12:19.408 --> 01:12:23.575
Even though she would love
it if I was, wouldn't you?

01:12:27.659 --> 01:12:29.576
- Don't do this, Scott.

01:12:30.634 --> 01:12:31.467
- Do what?

01:12:32.874 --> 01:12:34.427
Huh?

01:12:34.427 --> 01:12:35.756
- Don't do this.

01:12:35.756 --> 01:12:36.589
- Do what?

01:12:38.944 --> 01:12:42.111
Make you choose the way that I had to?

01:12:43.442 --> 01:12:45.215
What about him?

01:12:45.215 --> 01:12:46.706
What about him, huh?

01:12:46.706 --> 01:12:49.120
Should we make him choose?

01:12:49.120 --> 01:12:51.423
What do you think, Tim?

01:12:51.423 --> 01:12:54.340
You wanna know what I went through?

01:12:55.999 --> 01:12:56.832
Okay.

01:12:58.255 --> 01:12:59.943
Let's play.

01:12:59.943 --> 01:13:00.776
Let's...

01:13:04.047 --> 01:13:07.547
Everybody gets to be what they never were,

01:13:08.400 --> 01:13:10.317
so me, I'm the monster.

01:13:12.928 --> 01:13:15.011
And you, you're the fool.

01:13:20.627 --> 01:13:22.294
And you, the victim.

01:13:29.262 --> 01:13:30.878
It's gonna be fun.

01:13:39.672 --> 01:13:43.172
You never have really been here, have you?

01:13:46.405 --> 01:13:48.723
Always just telling stories, right?

01:13:48.723 --> 01:13:51.973
Just stealing other people's tragedies,

01:13:53.556 --> 01:13:56.389
but you never had one of your own.

01:13:59.061 --> 01:14:03.061
You know, maybe that is
your greatest suffering,

01:14:04.611 --> 01:14:08.028
and maybe I can help you with that, yeah?

01:14:10.213 --> 01:14:13.157
Okay, what do you say, huh?

01:14:13.157 --> 01:14:14.259
Should I slit her throat?

01:14:14.259 --> 01:14:17.012
- Please, please, Scott, don't do this.

01:14:17.012 --> 01:14:18.014
- But why?

01:14:18.014 --> 01:14:19.715
She was gonna do it to you.

01:14:19.715 --> 01:14:20.548
She was.

01:14:21.748 --> 01:14:24.515
She just wanted me to see.

01:14:24.515 --> 01:14:27.893
You didn't know what I was capable of.

01:14:27.893 --> 01:14:30.643
You didn't know what you made me.

01:14:34.198 --> 01:14:37.019
- I didn't make you anything.

01:14:39.819 --> 01:14:42.106
- You didn't put the blade in my hand?

01:14:42.106 --> 01:14:44.570
You didn't push me to the edge?

01:14:44.570 --> 01:14:46.475
You didn't catch me on a downturn

01:14:46.475 --> 01:14:50.748
and just play me like
you did everybody else.

01:14:50.748 --> 01:14:55.195
Okay, one question, how
long would I have had?

01:15:00.609 --> 01:15:01.947
Hmm?

01:15:01.947 --> 01:15:02.780
- Please.

01:15:05.010 --> 01:15:05.843
Scott.

01:15:14.361 --> 01:15:15.278
I'm scared.

01:15:16.193 --> 01:15:17.026
- Good.

01:15:18.894 --> 01:15:21.977
You actually look like a human being.

01:15:23.195 --> 01:15:27.362
All the suffering and
tragedy that you have caused.

01:15:31.775 --> 01:15:33.358
This is my justice.

01:15:37.696 --> 01:15:39.706
This is my revenge.

01:15:43.686 --> 01:15:44.519
Hey, O.

01:15:48.047 --> 01:15:48.880
Stay.

01:15:49.983 --> 01:15:51.183
Stay.

01:15:52.581 --> 01:15:53.843
Don't worry, buddy.

01:15:53.843 --> 01:15:55.843
I'm just making a point.

01:15:58.479 --> 01:16:00.396
What do you think, Tim?

01:16:01.327 --> 01:16:04.910
If you had a choice,
would you die for her?

01:16:05.791 --> 01:16:06.880
Would you?

01:16:06.880 --> 01:16:09.422
- I don't know.

01:16:09.422 --> 01:16:11.589
- It's not an answer, Tim.

01:16:12.814 --> 01:16:14.383
You need to make a choice
or you're gonna die,

01:16:14.383 --> 01:16:15.383
both of you.

01:16:15.383 --> 01:16:18.181
And I'm gonna be the one
who walks out of here,

01:16:18.181 --> 01:16:19.648
so why don't you make the choice

01:16:19.648 --> 01:16:21.731
that I never got to make?

01:16:23.422 --> 01:16:25.172
- You had the choice.

01:16:26.517 --> 01:16:28.655
- Oh, that's right.

01:16:28.655 --> 01:16:30.190
You were there.

01:16:30.190 --> 01:16:31.986
What did I say?

01:16:31.986 --> 01:16:33.344
What did I do?

01:16:33.344 --> 01:16:35.087
Because the more that I think about it,

01:16:35.087 --> 01:16:38.087
the more that I just can't remember.

01:16:40.222 --> 01:16:43.472
All right, Tim, let's make that choice.

01:16:44.511 --> 01:16:46.594
All one, make the choice.

01:16:52.388 --> 01:16:53.391
- No.

01:16:53.391 --> 01:16:55.456
- Right answer.

01:17:10.551 --> 01:17:12.743
What's the matter?

01:17:12.743 --> 01:17:13.993
Beat you to it?

01:17:16.440 --> 01:17:18.440
This is what you wanted.

01:17:20.311 --> 01:17:24.007
This is want you wanted me to become.

01:17:41.984 --> 01:17:45.151
This is how I want you to remember it.

01:17:49.784 --> 01:17:50.784
- Thank you.

01:17:56.298 --> 01:17:57.803
- Now run.

01:18:40.309 --> 01:18:42.226
Say it, say it, say it.

01:18:46.831 --> 01:18:48.164
Kill me, say it.

01:18:52.705 --> 01:18:53.538
Say it.

01:18:55.223 --> 01:18:56.515
Say it.

01:18:56.515 --> 01:18:57.348
Kill me.

01:18:58.497 --> 01:18:59.499
Kill me.

01:19:28.763 --> 01:19:31.100
- You all right, there?

01:19:38.123 --> 01:19:40.604
Ma'am, are you all right?

01:19:40.604 --> 01:19:41.437
- Perfect.

01:19:51.718 --> 01:19:55.083
It was someone I thought I could trust,

01:19:55.083 --> 01:19:58.166
share myself with and know in return.

01:20:02.491 --> 01:20:03.824
But I was wrong.

01:20:07.035 --> 01:20:10.702
The real monsters are
the ones we don't see.

01:20:12.475 --> 01:20:14.892
Standing right in front of us

01:20:16.507 --> 01:20:18.424
and then it's too late.

01:20:21.594 --> 01:20:24.844
I just keep seeing him reaching for me,

01:20:28.726 --> 01:20:31.809
trying to squeeze the life out of me,

01:20:33.238 --> 01:20:36.571
and I wonder who that person really was?

01:20:44.109 --> 01:20:44.942
- I know.

01:20:47.661 --> 01:20:51.161
It's hard to let anybody touch me anymore.

01:20:54.659 --> 01:20:55.908
Even a hand on the shoulder,

01:20:55.908 --> 01:20:57.636
trying to be supportive is a trigger.

01:20:57.636 --> 01:20:58.884
Just keeps bringing me back.

01:20:58.884 --> 01:21:00.584
I want to be okay with it,

01:21:00.584 --> 01:21:03.501
but people don't seem to understand

01:21:04.675 --> 01:21:06.931
and if I try to explain myself,

01:21:06.931 --> 01:21:11.076
I just come off as crazy, or I don't know.

01:21:19.140 --> 01:21:20.307
- Not for you?

01:21:21.781 --> 01:21:24.003
- I don't think it's quite
for anyone, honestly.

01:21:24.003 --> 01:21:25.556
- How so?

01:21:25.556 --> 01:21:28.340
- Relies too much on the past.

01:21:28.340 --> 01:21:31.007
What happened, what we remember.

01:21:32.696 --> 01:21:35.507
Those things can change
however we want them.

01:21:43.602 --> 01:21:46.385
- So what do you hold on to?

01:21:46.385 --> 01:21:47.885
- What comes next.

01:21:49.394 --> 01:21:50.311
Going down?

01:21:51.968 --> 01:21:53.794
- I'll take another.

